doc.after: Gyeongju lies in the southeastern corner of North Gyeongsang Province, and is bounded by the metropolitan city of Ulsan on the south. Within the province, its neighbors include Pohang on the north, Cheongdo County on the southwest, and Yeongcheon on the northwest.[2] Gyeongju is located about 50 kilometers (31Â mi) north of Busan.[3] To the east, it has no neighbor but the sea.[2]
